                     <interp inst="t18490409-924-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18490409-924-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>, stealing 1 handkerchief, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of a man unknown, from his person: having been before convicted.</rs>
